{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/using-ffmpeg-to-convert-a-mov-viedo-to-a-gif-image","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6840e249-371e-5e8f-b61e-f1ab8e712cef","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/4b190/movie-gif.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/8ac56/movie-gif.webp 240w,\n/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/d3be9/movie-gif.webp 480w,\n/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/d00b9/movie-gif.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/09b79/movie-gif.jpg 240w,\n/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/7cc5e/movie-gif.jpg 480w,\n/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/4b190/movie-gif.jpg 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/4b190/movie-gif.jpg\"\n            alt=\"movie-gif\"\n            title=\"movie-gif\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>FFmpeg</strong> is a free and open-source software project consisting of a suite of libraries and programs for handling video, audio, and other multimedia files and streams. It’s a powerful tool for professionals and enthusiasts.</p>\n<p><strong>FFmpeg</strong> can decode a file of its supported formats and reencode it. This feature could be used to convert file formats. Furthermore, FFmpeg supports for various filters enhances its utility in refining the output. Filters such as ‘scale’, ‘fps’, and ‘palettegen’ can integrated into the conversion process, allowing users to manipulate the dimensions, frame rate, and color palette.</p>\n<p>A practical implementation of FFmpeg for converting a MOV video to a GIF image can be elucidated through the provided <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/SheldonWangRJT/8d3f44a35c8d1386a396b9b49b43c385\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">code snippet</a>. Command line could be,</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ ffmpeg -i input.mov -pix_fmt rgb8 -r <span class=\"token number\">10</span> output.gif</code></pre></div>\n<p>The example code take <em>RGB8</em> as the output codec (<code class=\"language-text\">-pix_fmt rgb8</code>), and set frame rate to <em>10 Hz</em> (<code class=\"language-text\">-r 10</code>) to reduce size. As <code class=\"language-text\">-f</code> is not specified, the <em>ffmpeg</em> binary will guess the format on file extension, so the output will be automatically set to GIF image in the example.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/using-ffmpeg-to-convert-a-mov-viedo-to-a-gif-image","tagSlugs":["/tag/multimedia/","/tag/f-fmpeg/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2023-12-20T13:10:00.000Z","description":"a guide of using FFmpeg to convert a MOV Viedo to a GIF image.","tags":["Multimedia","FFmpeg"],"title":"Using FFmpeg to Convert a MOV Viedo to a GIF Image","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/8e27f8b5ac257a1dea194272f23ad0f9/movie-gif.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/using-ffmpeg-to-convert-a-mov-viedo-to-a-gif-image"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}